   <text>
      <body>
        <div>
            <pb facs="#TL-0597.jpg" n="part4_p123.jpg" xml:id="img_0123" corresp="https://id.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/tillich-lectures/part4_p123.jpg"/>
            
            <p facs="#facs_123_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>[592]
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>called upon to fight not only against the abuse of drinking, alcoholic drinking, but also to introduce
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>special <rs type="keyword" ref="#Law">law</rs>s, special techniques, to suppress it, in the moment of rohibition [sic.]. Nothing has more
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>damaged the <rs type="keyword" ref="#Authority">authority</rs> of the <church>Church</church>'s message than their simple identification of what they had to
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_5" n="N005"/>say, with a special law of the <rs type="keyword" ref="#State">state</rs> which proved to be, after a certain time, only an immense and
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_6" n="N006"/>unhoped-for gift for all gangs[ters], in this country. <hi style="font-style: italic;">[little laughter]</hi> So the Church has to state the
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_7" n="N007"/>principles, negatively and positively, but the Church cannot, AS CHURCH, speak about the
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>remedies. And we <rs type="keyword" ref="#Religious_socialism">religious socialists</rs> were VERY MUCH aware of this. We never said that our
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>analysis of the time, our suggestions of transformation, are identical with the message of <rs type="keyword" ref="#Jesus_as_the_Christ">Jesus-as-
               <lb break="no" facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_10" n="N010"/>the-Christ</rs>. But AS <rs type="keyword" ref="#Christianity">CHRISTIANS</rs>, we dared to fall into error and to make statements daringly,
               <lb facs="#facs_123_tr_1_tl_11" n="N011"/>and [to] be judged by <rs type="keyword" ref="#History">history</rs> itself. And we WERE!
            </p>
            
        </div>
